Pickle Rick TryHackMe Writeup This is a blog on how i solved Pickle Rick room on tryhackme. Note that i use linux. First i put the machine IP into env using the export command.
export IP=(your target machine&#39;s IP addres) Enum Nmap I did a simple nmap scan on the server:
nmap -sCV -oN nmap-init.log $IP -sCV is for using the default scripts and check for services version on the machine.
